cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech technology and language acquisition. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it involves processing of audio data. The use of Bayesian models and Gibbs samplers suggests it could also be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.SI (Signal Processing).
